# Faith tab “Load full passage” uses https://bible-api.com (WEB, public domain) — no key required.

# --- Supabase project setup (Dashboard / CLI) ---
# 1) Authentication → Providers → enable Anonymous sign-ins (required for plan + daily hero).
# 2) Edge Function secrets (never put these in the Expo app):
#    supabase secrets set OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-... SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...
#    (Do not use the SUPABASE_ prefix for custom secrets — it is reserved.)
# 3) Apply SQL migrations: from this folder run `supabase db push` when your network supports IPv4 to the DB host.
#    If the CLI fails with IPv6 errors, open SQL Editor and run the files in supabase/migrations in name order.
